\v 32 the sons of Meedda, the sons of Coutha, the sons of Charea, the sons of Barchue, the sons of Serar, the sons of Thomi, the sons of Nasith, the sons of Atepha. 
\p  
\v 33 Solomon, the sons of him \sls (or The sons of Solomon’s servants)\sls*; the sons of Asapphioth, the sons of Pharida, the sons of Jeeli, the sons of Lozon, the sons of Isdael, the sons of Saphythi, 
\p  
